-=[ Mage Council Duties ]=-

The Responsibities of the Mage Council are as follows:
+ Maintain Order and Morale within the Guild.
+ Recruit new players for the Guild.
+ Teach and Guide current members of the Guild.
+ Settle disputes between Guild members.
+ Award members for superior performance in the Guild and penalize
  those members that take actions the hurt the guild.

Council member duties include, but are non limited to, these duties.

